data.description: Embrace tranquility and elegance while touring this exquisite home! Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, offering over 3,500 sqft, the highlight of this home is its expansive primary suite with large custom built closet, nook for a work space, private balcony to overlook backyard, and its enormous ensuite for unwinding and relaxing in soaking tub after those long days.  1st floor ensuite is currently used as an office space with custom cabinetry and work desk. Enjoy creating your own culinary masterpieces in your dream kitchen and sit at an enormous bar to sip your morning joe! Large living room in view from kitchen and separate dining area for warm family dinners. Plenty of storage space and large walk in closets plus the oversized storage shed. Bonus recreational space with wet bar for entertaining family & friends.  This home is a perfect blend of comfort and elegance!
